description:
Daddies Manuel Skye and Jonas Jackson like to keep things exciting in their marriage. And, after a dreadful day at work, Jonas has a surprise waiting for Manuel in the bath - Russian hustler Austin Sugar.

When the men are ready to play, Austin gets suited and things get really hot, rough and dirty. A raw threesome that combines trouser ripping, ass eating, flip flop fucking and a facial for the suited hustler.
title: MEN AT PLAY: Suited Hustler
